OL,3,CConcerns around local election vote
OL,4,Ccounting process to be investigated
OL,6,FAn investigation will take place after
OL,7,Fconcerns were raised around the count
OL,8,Fprocess in a Calderdale Council ward
OL,9,Fin May's local elections.
OL,11,FOn May 8 those keeping an eye on the
OL,12,Fvoting for the ward of Rastrick near
OL,13,FBrighouse saw the vote re-declared
OL,14,Fsome time after the winning
OL,15,Fcouncillors were announced due to an
OL,16,F'administrative error'.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
