PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779196276
OL,3,CConcerns around local election vote
OL,4,Ccounting process to be investigated
OL,6,FThe mix up did not affect the outcome
OL,7,Fof the contest, which saw Reform UK's
OL,8,FSimon Briggs, Dave Small and Jackie
OL,9,FWilson elected as councillors for
OL,10,FRastrick.
OL,12,FIt was part of a successful day for
OL,13,FReform in Calderdale who took full
OL,14,Fcontrol of the council, ousting Labour.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/6
